{"_path":"/resident/r033","_dir":"resident","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"A7重劃區 行政里規劃 草案","description":null,"image":"/images/resident/r033-01.jpeg","sequence":33,"category":"地方行政","place":"A7重劃區","author":"社區網站","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2025 "},{"name":"og:title","content":"社區網站-地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-03-27T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"a7-重劃區-行政里規劃-草案"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區 行政里規劃 草案"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"主旨"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主旨"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區是人口快速成長的區域, 希望能依據前瞻性地方發展做宏觀區域鄰里規劃。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"說明"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"說明"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"a7-重劃區目前發展上的問題"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區目前發展上的問題"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"由於 A7 重劃區的人口增長遠遠超出政府的預期, 市府的各項生活配套措施都無法跟上人口的成長。主要包含下列議題："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"區域公車的路線/班次規劃沒有依據社區的成長做前瞻性彈性調整, 公車業者只依據原有路線的平均載客人次作為增班依據。造成居民與業者雙輸的惡性循環。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"區域內綠地公園及運動設施嚴重不足。 區域滯洪池的活化利用的作業也極其緩慢, 遠遠不及林口的滯洪池活化成效。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"目前四個里都屬於新舊社區混合狀態。民政局仍以統一 5,000 戶標準作為\"應\"分里的依據。 殊不知重劃區的里長服務不需對應每戶而是對應社區為單位。 大型社區可能超過一千戶, 通常十多個社區就會達到 5,000 戶。 在行政資源方面如文青里剛剛完成里民活動中心的設計，又要分里造成資源的爭奪問題。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"區域內仍有許多待建土地及施工中的工地。由於市府的環境維護沒有做好源頭管制, 造成區域垃圾永遠清理不完。除文青里外其他里長的志工多屬於舊社區, 似乎無法有效因應新社區的環保需求。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"重劃區內各項設施都屬缺乏，如里民活動中心,圖書館, 公共托兒所等等。相關的居民活動如各項球類, 健身, 娛樂等都急需對重劃區做長遠的前瞻規劃而不是變形蟲式的太大就切兩段。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"a7-重劃區的現有行政里-202502"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區的現有行政里 2025/02"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如 A7 社區網站 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://a7kanban15.netlify.app/introduction/a7"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"城市探索 - A7 重劃區 地區介紹"}]},{"type":"text","value":": A7 重劃區分屬於桃園市龜山區的 長庚里, 樂善里, 文化里及文青里 四個里。 至 2025 年 2 月 四個里的戶數及人口數如下表："}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"table","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"thead","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"單別"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"戶數"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"總人ロ數"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tbody","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善里"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"10,412"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"19,491"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文化里"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"5,136"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"10,284"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"長庚里"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3,655"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"7,233"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文青里"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"6,086"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"11,941"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"合計"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"25,289"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"48,949"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"註: 平均每戶 1.94 人/戶"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_2025-年民政局分里作業"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2025 年民政局分里作業"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"民政局即將在「2025/04/09」於桃園市議會進行工作報告及說明。 該日會議應該會討論到「桃園市鄰里調整」的相關事務。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"依據 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/life/breakingnews/4766592?fbclid=IwY2xjawJQ5CJleHRuA2FlbQIxMQABHTM-3mSIvFO0a2jwxOnheWIVwicIIsjxlOoImfYv_CCrkVXp6i4hYQKpWQ_aem_41xyBLE22yIkGgEUx5lBTA"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自由時報 2024/08/12"}]},{"type":"text","value":":\n桃園市現有 516 個里，近年人口成長快速，尤其是桃園、中壢、龜山、八德等區的新興重劃區，統計約有 18 里已達分里標準，民政局表示， "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自治條例針對超過 3500 戶人口大里「得」分里"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，但無強制性，但在市府原則下，考量里長負荷及服務品質， "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"5000 戶人口大里則「應」分里"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，此次龜山區樂善（8674 戶）、文青（5847 戶）2 里、已完成規畫分里提報。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"其中，樂善里位於龜山 A7 重劃區內，截至 2024 年 7 月，全里已有 8674 戶、1 萬 6842 萬人，比復興區 4015 戶、總人口數 1 萬 3166 人還多，是桃園市最大里，而樂善里過去歷經多次重分，像是現在的長庚里，因林口長庚醫護社區進駐，20 多年前即從樂善分出，近年因 A7 重劃區開發，2018 年再分出文青里，相較 2022 年地方選舉時戶數約 5700 戶、人口數 1 萬 1000 多人，人口在短短 1 年多成長迅速，因此再次啟動分里規畫。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善里長黃錦芳說，「人口增加、該分就要分」，他支持分里，分里前公所也有跟地方溝通，里內戶數逾 8000 戶，對里長工作是很大的考驗，"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"依據 文青里"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/15wP8FtGTH/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"里長 謝嘉仁 FB 2025/03/24"}]},{"type":"text","value":": 因為剛剛完成規劃的里民活動中心會有爭議, 許多里內公共建設的推動剛剛起步。 發起 「文青不分里」連署活動, 文青里里長希望爭取不分里。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r033-01.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r033-01.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"辦法"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"辦法"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"a7-重劃區行政里規劃建議"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區行政里規劃建議"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"目前分里作業似乎是在變形蟲的方式, 每隔一段時間過大的里就一分為二。 這種方式會造成戶籍資料的重複變更！ 針對 A7 重劃區是否能一次做全盤規劃 將 A7 重劃區分為五個里:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"人口規模"}]},{"type":"text","value":"： 依據區域內建案預估戶數做前瞻式規劃, 並預留各里的未來增長空間, 以求一勞永逸。"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"由於重劃區人口密集, 里長可以以社區為單位分層服務, 建議能適度擴大里的戶數"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"地理範圍"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：目前已有五大生活圈, 如過作為分里的主要依據將可簡化地圖修訂作業。 如下圖所示, 重劃區的密度會讓各里面積不致于過大。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"社區凝聚力"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：建置時會考慮新社區的生活圈, 可以增強公車, 公園綠化, 環保志工等各項議題的意見整合。 目前除了文青里是以新社區為主外, 其他里的志工多是舊社區居民組成。希望未來能以新社區為主體才能強化志工的參與。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"行政需求"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：未來的里民活動中心在人口數尚未成長期間, 可以考量整併建設, 如上中下三個區塊。 共享行政里/活動中心等資源。 在每一里都有民眾活動中心的前提, 不宜將里劃分太小。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r033-02.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r033-02.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"下面是依據現有建案規模預估至 2028 年的個生活圈戶數, 在中心商業區及文青國小區未來都會超出現有 5,000 戶, 應該考量重劃區的人口蜜度較高不宜比照舊社區的標準："}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"table","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"thead","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"行政里"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"住家戶數"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"商店戶數"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"事務所數"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tbody","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善國小生活圈"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3,429"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"140"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"郵政物流園區"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"4,354"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"57"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"中心商業區"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"8,237"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"218"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"110"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文青國小生活圈"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"7,154"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"186"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"118"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"體育大學生活圈"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"5,935"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"31"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r031-22.png","src":"/images/resident/r031-22.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_2025-年度修訂的建議做法"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2025 年度修訂的建議做法"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"年度修訂已提報文青及樂善 兩個里, 建議將現有樂善里直接分爲三個里"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"現有樂善里舊社區"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"郵政物流園區 + 樂善國小生活圈 （但扣除現有長庚里）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"中心商業區 （但扣除現有文化里）+ 文青國小生活圈"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這三個里到 2028 年都會再次超過 5,000 戶！ 到時候可做第二次修訂就能達到本文建議的理想結構。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在此期間讓 A7 重劃區分上中下三大區塊, 建立行政資源如里民活動中心等。 現有文青里建構的里民活動中心可暫時提供體育大學生活圈加上舊社區使用，也能滿足現任文青里長的訴求。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"a7-重劃區-行政里規劃-草案","depth":2,"text":"A7 重劃區 行政里規劃 草案"},{"id":"主旨","depth":2,"text":"主旨"},{"id":"說明","depth":2,"text":"說明","children":[{"id":"a7-重劃區目前發展上的問題","depth":3,"text":"A7 重劃區目前發展上的問題"},{"id":"a7-重劃區的現有行政里-202502","depth":3,"text":"A7 重劃區的現有行政里 2025/02"},{"id":"_2025-年民政局分里作業","depth":3,"text":"2025 年民政局分里作業"}]},{"id":"辦法","depth":2,"text":"辦法","children":[{"id":"a7-重劃區行政里規劃建議","depth":3,"text":"A7 重劃區行政里規劃建議"},{"id":"_2025-年度修訂的建議做法","depth":3,"text":"2025 年度修訂的建議做法"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:resident:r033.md","_source":"content","_file":"resident/r033.md","_extension":"md"}